{"tid":1089268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局　頻入市　銀行結餘已洗走3分之2　無公布　非常異常","createTime":"2019-04-02T16:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T17:50:58.000Z","uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a53a66858478fbf0c1e978b16132594e049c4f58","tid":1089268,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156623718069934&amp;set=a.10156336969309934&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156623718069934%26set%3Da.10156336969309934%26type%3D3&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BjBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=aaa8b1b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156623718069934&amp;set=a.10156336969309934&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156623718069934&amp;set=a.10156336969309934&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10156623718069934%26set%3Da.10156336969309934%26type%3D3&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2BjBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=aaa8b1b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10156623718069934&amp;set=a.10156336969309934&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n我諗好多人都冇留意呢啲消息，其實銀行體系結餘由去年$1800億，不斷俾人「洗劫」，這幾個星期速度超級加快，而且好狠好兇！剛才又冇咗50億，現在剩返540億！（早兩日仲有680億）<br />\n<br />\n「颱風」將至，大家請提醒身邊朋友做好「防風措施」，各安天命，好自為之。<img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tfb/1/16/1f64f_1f3fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftfb%2F1%2F16%2F1f64f_1f3fb.png&h=1e4801cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tfb/1/16/1f64f_1f3fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ftfb%2F1%2F16%2F1f64f_1f3fb.png&h=1e4801cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruxz7S2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fruxz7S2.jpg&h=c1b74128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPak Chai<br />\n咁即係有人，將大量資產帶離開香港。<br />\n問題係點解，樓市同埋股市都冇下跌？<br />\n<br />\nDanny Lam<br />\nPak Chai 係主流傳媒刻意暫時不大肆報導。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMartin Shin<br />\n個人愚見: 金管局接咗港元沽盤(此的確會令銀行體系港元結餘下降) ，仍可透過外滙基金票據、外滙基金債券等工具把銀根放鬆。再者，不是一定要用港元交易或/及結算。<br />\n<br />\nBenson Tsang<br />\nMartin Shin ，我一向不是「財經頻道」的人，過去咁多年也甚少分享經濟消息。政府￼庫儲備的確豐厚，也有好多方法將銀根放鬆，但係這個post 的主要目的, 係講緊「大量資金流走」這個經濟訊號，香港是外向型經濟體，也沒有外匯管制，資金流入流出是平常事，但係在短短一年之間流出左三分之二（又去年1800億至現在跌破600億），這個數目絕對不是尋常現象，這也是一個「訊號」，而最奇怪的事，政府和金管局，異常低調處理這件事。在退後一步，如果金融震盪，又或者港幣被追擊，大家能否相信政府官員、陳茂波同金管局有能力處理金融危機。<br />\n<br />\nKeylive Lay<br />\n以前每當港元有不利消息，金融管理局都會出來宣布有關訊息，並以什麼什麼方式作應急措施，大派定心丸畀市民大眾及市場，呢幾次幾乎是沒有宣布，點解？！"},{"pid":"cec0b1c87706ee00b6f3de6f2d1146d3f485bee0","tid":1089268,"uid":191926,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"問題是幾時加息"},{"pid":"5bef74ca7ac690fb1b2a43a18cdc97fff38ad38f","tid":1089268,"uid":51620,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為逃犯條例班白鬼走定資先？"},{"pid":"8412c8c3e0d4526a830fda63247ad9f99125c6ac","tid":1089268,"uid":62527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"36e1e341caaa01a398846848facdd93284bc209f","tid":1089268,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"食息差呀on9"},{"pid":"fe6d31ea1cd0256433162d39e4fe402231e7e300","tid":1089268,"uid":34863,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔想佢爆<br />\n但班低能連聯匯係乜都唔知出嚟獻世"},{"pid":"3f3a50c6ae710828781a47ae1127475e49468946","tid":1089268,"uid":242630,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"又係你呀阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早兩日連銀行儲備同銀行體系結餘都未識分出黎扮專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比人笑到面黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁快又出黎求世？真係好有青山走犯Feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199ff8097f6bd67e95786e2d7646c635e5db8dc1","tid":1089268,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bef74ca7ac690fb1b2a43a18cdc97fff38ad38f","tid":1089268,"uid":51620,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為逃犯條例班白鬼走定資先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f593365303bd47289f7b6bea08fa411c2e6c8be","tid":1089268,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T16:50:01.000Z","msg":"關係法88"},{"pid":"2f8441b80c1991e8144ac14b88c5526f77d6431a","tid":1089268,"uid":212796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"青山開放週？"},{"pid":"10d9821b56074f6d931f82ed7951839fef0f2688","tid":1089268,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"有冇經濟學家講下兩者咩關係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}